      <div class="bulk-builds__container--narrow">
        <h2>Ready to level up dinner?</h2>
        <p>Load your cart with ICON bulk staples, remix them your way, then tag <strong>@iconmeals</strong> with <strong>#EverydayICON</strong>. We feature the best plates every week.</p>
